ely amazed by the fact that a married woman with kids could write so badly and just couldn't contain himself.  I don't blame him one bit, you come to this board to begin a dialogue and then annoy people who actually click on your post to read your dribble?  <br>
<br>
If I wanted to get off a kos list, I'd make sure those I'm asking off the list could at least read the request with minimal difficulty.  This is a game, but it's a game that requires communication.  Communication is best achieved when people write or speak clearly.  Try it sometime. <p><!--EZCODE IMAGE START--><img src="http://home.earthlink.net/~nmenasch/kyle.gif"/><!--EZCODE IMAGE END--><br>
