<br>
Yes, you can talk anyway you like.  Yes, you can use abbreviations, contractions, run on sentences, etc.  You also have the right to look like a complete moron.<br>
<br>
I think this would be a good place to practice proper English, or at least make an effort.  Unless your aspirations are to be appointed to the drive-through window by Mayor McCheese.<br>
